'''百草路站'''位于[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]][[四川省|四川省]][[成都市|成都市]][[郫都区|郫都区]]百草路，是[[成都地铁2号线|成都地铁2号线]]的地下车站<ref>{{cite news| title =犀浦站百草路站首次亮相 2号线西延线下月正式开通| publisher =四川在线| date =2013-05-23| url =http://sichuan.scol.com.cn/cddt/content/2013-05/23/content_5269426.htm| accessdate =2013-05-23| language =zh| archive-date =2017-12-12| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171212035944/http://sichuan.scol.com.cn/cddt/content/2013-05/23/content_5269426.htm| dead-url =no}}</ref>，于2013年6月8日开通使用<ref name="启用">{{cite news | title =成都地铁2号线西延线今日正式开通试运营(组图) | publisher =腾讯大成网 | date =2013-06-08 | url =http://cd.qq.com/a/20130608/018042.htm | accessdate =2013-06-08 | language =zh | archive-date =2017-12-12 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171212091219/http://cd.qq.com/a/20130608/018042.htm | dead-url =no }}</ref>。在2号线西延线建设期间，本站曾使用工程名“外语学校站”<ref>{{cite news | title =地铁2号线西延线进场施工 | publisher =网易 | date =2010-09-16 | url =http://news.163.com/10/0916/05/6GM99OUH00014AED.html | accessdate =2010-09-16 | language =zh | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171212031425/http://news.163.com/10/0916/05/6GM99OUH00014AED.html | archive-date =2017-12-12 | dead-url =yes }}</ref>。因为工程实际建设情况的变化，本站比设计之初向东移动约200米<ref>{{cite news | title =成都地铁2号线东西延线5座车站位置有变 | publisher =腾讯大成网 | date =2012-08-13 | url =http://cd.qq.com/a/20120813/000326.htm | accessdate =2012-08-13 | language =zh | archive-date =2017-12-12 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171212084151/http://cd.qq.com/a/20120813/000326.htm | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

